{"tid":2348702,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"發展局：正探討可否於另一海濱地點重置皇后碼頭","createTime":"2021-01-01T03:03:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T11:56:56.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"bc7c2c47cb0e8b85c9b4fffd436066a4e281d091","tid":2348702,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T03:03:54.000Z","msg":"《明報》報道，發展局正探討在另一個海濱位置，重置已於2007年被清拆的皇后碼頭。<br />\n<br />\n發展局回覆查詢時亦表示，現正探討是否可以在其中一個優化海濱項目下，在另一個海濱位置，重置皇后碼頭，並恢復其碼頭功能。<br />\n<br />\n發展局表示，在未來數年，當局都會推行多個優化海濱項目。政府已在2016年時，在中環9號和10號碼頭之間，就重置皇后碼頭的設計方案進行公眾諮詢，政府正按收集到的意見，詳細考慮未來路向。"},{"pid":"eb101db68635f03eeee85db06a1ca0f1ea47e085","tid":2348702,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T03:03:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1568165-20210101.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1568165-20210101.htm&d=h8K6dYNnEA4rSgnLcindhVm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=63d636d3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1568165-20210101.htm&h=e2d6825b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1568165-20210101.htm</a>"},{"pid":"dc83f1d23f3e35264b33111a050a68054d27d55b","tid":2348702,"uid":106,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T03:05:22.000Z","msg":"16年扮唔知扮到而家又話要保育<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66fdfa4f7f10ea5307f1655832fd3969ae902b51","tid":2348702,"uid":78971,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dc83f1d23f3e35264b33111a050a68054d27d55b","tid":2348702,"uid":106,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T03:05:22.000Z","msg":"16年扮唔知扮到而家又話要保育<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T03:07:13.000Z","msg":"失去咗先學人講保育<br />\n早抖啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\